						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Stone lying in Survey No. 8.</hi></p>						

						<p>[Siṅghaṇa]—A.D. 1207.</p>						

						<p>This record is dated in the king's regnal <hi rend="bold">year 1, Prabhava, Chaitra, śu. 1, Sunday.</hi> The <hi rend="italic">tithi</hi> corresponds to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1207, March 1.</hi> The weekday was, however, Thursday.</p>						

						<p>The inscription records a gift made by Sōvagauḍa and Haṁḍe gauḍa to Maseyanāyaka.</p>						

						</summary>
